    "Table 3 Summary of latest works based on brain morphology Author Year Advantages Disadvantages Brain region Fuse et al. (2018) 2018 The current research suggests that shape information, as opposed to traditional volume ratio, is more helpful in diagnosis A thorough analysis of the traits for classification and interpretation, however, is omitted in the work Lateral ventricle, excluding the septum lucidum Aruchamy et al.",
